      "skill2": {
        "skillName": "Blood and Bones",
        "stat": "will",
        "definition": "<p>By casting bones in a bowl filled with blood&nbsp;drawn from a person, the Druid can alter&nbsp;the fate of that person. The Druid rolls Blood&nbsp;and Bones against a DC:10 + the target&rsquo;s&nbsp;WILL. On a success, the target can add half&nbsp;the Druid&rsquo;s Blood and Bones value to one&nbsp;check made before the next sunrise. <br>On a failure, the target cannot benefit from this ability for 1 week.&nbsp;A single target can only&nbsp;benefit from this ability once per session.</p>",
