      "skill2": {
        "skillName": "Sacred Grove",
        "stat": "will",
        "definition": "<p>A Druid can turn an area of nature into a&nbsp;sacred grove. This takes 1 hour, and covers&nbsp;an area with a 20m radius. The Druid&nbsp;takes the value of their Sacred Grove check&nbsp;and uses those points to add protections&nbsp;to their sacred grove. The Druid and&nbsp;anyone they specify are immune to these&nbsp;protections. This grove lasts for 3 months&nbsp;and the Druid can maintain a number of&nbsp;groves equal to their Sacred Grove value.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Overgrown Enviroment</strong></span><strong><br></strong><strong>Cost:</strong> 2<br>The plants of the area grow wildly out of control, imposing a -2 to Dodge/Escape, and Athletics checsks.</li>\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Lost<br></strong></span><strong>Cost:</strong> 10<br>A magical fog settles aroudn the grove which forces anyone entering it to make a DC: 16 Resist Magic check to enter the area. Targets who fail are turned around and immediately exit the grove.</li>\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Poisoned Harvest</strong></span><strong><br></strong><strong>Cost:</strong> 6<br>Deadly magic suffuses the palnts of the grove causing crops grown in the area to inflict the poison effect when eaten.</li>\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Miracle Harvest<br></strong></span><strong>Cost:</strong> 4<br>The plants of the grove grow a bountiful harvest doubling the number of plant-based ingredients gather from each Foraging check.</li>\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Thorns</strong></span><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><br></span></strong><strong>Cost:</strong> 10<br>A wall of thorny vines sprouts at the edge of the grove and anything that passes through it must make a DC: 16 Athletics check or suffer the Bleeding condition.</li>\n</ul>",
